Subject: Re: [PATCH] ssb: Fix regression in 2.6.23-git3 due to change in calling add_uevent_var
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
